General.Name: ProPetro Holding Corp
General.Description: ProPetro Holding Corp. operates as an integrated oilfield services company. It offers hydraulic fracturing, wireline, cementing, and other complementary oilfield completion services to oil and gas producers and non-oil and gas applications, such as general industrial projects and data centers located primarily in Texas and New Mexico. ProPetro Holding Corp. was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Midland, Texas.
